{"tid":1857943,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"黃埔花園第11期男住客確診　街坊嘆「中招也沒辦法，還是要上班」","createTime":"2020-02-02T12:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T14:11:48.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7a65de43056ee0dbe1b0d6637fcd313aec294558","tid":1857943,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200201/s00001/ffbc75b3f8fb66dc055386d4b8c960c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200201%2Fs00001%2Fffbc75b3f8fb66dc055386d4b8c960c5.jpg&h=cf27e5c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃埔花園有男住客確診新型冠狀病毒，屋苑昨晚（1月31日）已清洗，今（2月1日）亦有清潔工人洗街。（鍾妍攝）<br />\n<br />\n一名居於黃埔花園第11期一座的39歲男子，昨（1月31日）確診新型冠狀病毒，屋苑昨晚已作清洗，記者今（2月1日）在屋苑外見有清潔工人洗街。有居於同一屋苑的住戶表示，出入會遠離一座的範圍，但如患者曾在社區遊走，「也怕不了這麼多，還是要出門上班」。<br />\n<br />\n今早約11時，黃埔花園第11期一座外有兩名清潔外判工人洗地，其中一名清潔工稱，屋苑會恆常每月洗地，今次收到指示要先清洗11期一座外面。她說，用了漂白水洗地，公司有為員工提供口罩，工作時她都有佩戴，但公司沒提供護目鏡，「怕不到這麼多，搵食嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n一座地面有一間韓國食肆，員工表示，因已做好防護措施，不太擔心會染病，又指出農曆新年後，公司已要求她們佩戴口罩，面對客人亦有做足防護措施。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n住在第11期二座的周先生已退休，他說今日出門特意繞路，遠離一座。他表示，家裏的口罩都是很久以前的存貨，不知是否仍有效，會減少外出，家中亦有倒漂白水到廁所消毒。<br />\n<br />\n有居於一座的住客說，擔心受感染也沒辦法，他也不知是哪層住戶患病，認為政府若公布樓層單位，或會造成恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n居於鄰座的劉先生說，不能怕這麼多，要「中招也沒辦法，還是要上班」，稱自己會減少外出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200201/s00001/1580547717163/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E9%BB%83%E5%9F%94%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92%E7%AC%AC11%E6%9C%9F%E7%94%B7%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%A2%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8A%E5%98%86%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%AD%E6%8B%9B%E4%B9%9F%E6%B2%92%E8%BE%A6%E6%B3%95-%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%8A%E7%8F%AD%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200201%2Fs00001%2F1580547717163%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%259F%2594%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%259C%2592%25E7%25AC%25AC11%25E6%259C%259F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%259D%258A%25E5%2598%2586%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%258B%259B%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%25B2%2592%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%258F%25AD%25E3%2580%258D&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9EpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=005339cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200201%2Fs00001%2F1580547717163%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%259F%2594%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%259C%2592%25E7%25AC%25AC11%25E6%259C%259F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%259D%258A%25E5%2598%2586%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%258B%259B%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%25B2%2592%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%258F%25AD%25E3%2580%258D&h=2e3ca543\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200201/s00001/1580547717163/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E9%BB%83%E5%9F%94%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92%E7%AC%AC11%E6%9C%9F%E7%94%B7%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%A2%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8A%E5%98%86%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%AD%E6%8B%9B%E4%B9%9F%E6%B2%92%E8%BE%A6%E6%B3%95-%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%8A%E7%8F%AD%E3%80%8D</a>"},{"pid":"f0b9d77158ae6e38e233c9c7713c393af65afa8b","tid":1857943,"uid":316048,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:02:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇野阻到香港人番工</span>"},{"pid":"a4097f13521f8d0b49f224fe1fcd8c33295bcf5a","tid":1857943,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:07:26.000Z","msg":"冇骨氣 冇撚用"},{"pid":"48173e7f9f3f477c4ca5ad9f18e0f7aa822cd0ce","tid":1857943,"uid":72991,"like":